  <brief_title>A 5-year Longitudinal Observational Study of the Natural History and Management of Patients With HCC</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 5-year Longitudinal Observational Study of the Natural History and Management of Patients With Hepatocellular Carcinoma (HCC)</official_title>
