  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      TARGET-HCC is a longitudinal, observational study of patients being managed for HCC in usual
      clinical practice. TARGET-HCC will create a research registry of participants with HCC
      within academic and community real-world practices in order to assess the safety and
      effectiveness of the entire spectrum of current and future therapies across diverse
      populations.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
